# Session logs (may contain sensitive debugging info)
# NOTE: Session logs are kept in git by default for team collaboration
# If a session log contains sensitive data, review before commit or add to gitignore
# docs/sessions/*.md

# Replay data (may contain sensitive market data or positions)
